		<seg id="32">This type of innovative program is relevant for European as well as American orchestras.</seg>
		<seg id="33">The problem of youth and access to the performing arts exists on both sides of the Atlantic.</seg>
		<seg id="34">So does poor music education in state schools.</seg>
		<seg id="35">If orchestras don't look after their own futures, they may well not have one to look after.</seg>
