	<doc corpus="potet" docid="27" lang="en" origlang="fr" type="HT">
		<seg id="0">Is Europe stuck?</seg>
		<seg id="1">The current team of leaders has been an enormous disappointment.</seg>
		<seg id="2">But as they fade away, there could be some light at the end of the tunnel.</seg>
		<seg id="3">In Germany, Chancellor Angela Merkel is obviously more positive on Europe and more pro-reform than her predecessor, but she is tied up in a grand coalition.</seg>
