		<seg id="0">Authoritarians at the Gate</seg>
		<seg id="1">Last Thursday, judges at Indonesia's Central Jakarta Court sentenced me to one year in prison.</seg>
		<seg id="2">As the editor-in-chief of Tempo Weekly Newsmagazine , I am guilty, according to the court, of defaming a business tycoon named Tomy Winata by implying his possible involvement in a fire at Jakarta's South-East Asia textile market, and of fomenting riots by disseminating lies.</seg>
