		<seg id="23">America must instead mobilize international coalitions to address these shared threats and challenges.</seg>
		<seg id="24">The willingness of others to cooperate depends in part on their own self-interest, but also on the attractiveness of American positions.</seg>
		<seg id="25">That power to attract is what I call &quot;soft power.&quot;</seg>
