		<seg id="28">Soft power arises from the attractiveness of a country's culture, ideals, and policies.</seg>
		<seg id="29">Hard power will always remain vital, but soft power will become increasingly important in dealing with transnational issues whose resolution requires multilateral cooperation.</seg>
