		<seg id="37">The paradox of American power is that the largest power since Rome cannot achieve many of its objectives unilaterally in a global information age.</seg>
		<seg id="38">America needs to pay more attention to soft power and to multilateral cooperation.</seg>
		<seg id="39">That is the real lesson of September 11.</seg>
