		<seg id="58">Responsible authorities - buddy-buddy with operators</seg>
		<seg id="59">The procedure of the mobile operators is easy to understand, the entrance of another operator would mean increased competition, it would lead to a decrease in prices and hence to a decrease in their profits.</seg>
		<seg id="60">Why, then, make this entrance easy for such a competitor?</seg>
