		<seg id="3">AT A time when Swiss voters have called for a ban on the construction of minarets and there is widespread alarm over the supposed Islamisation of Europe, John Bowen, an American academic, has written an informed and measured account of whether Muslims can integrateâ€”and are integratingâ€”into one of the continentâ€™s most avowedly secular societies.</seg>
