		<seg id="16">They are not having the argument all their way.</seg>
		<seg id="17">Conservatives are suspicious of the very idea of a French or European Islam.</seg>
		<seg id="18">The thinkers and activists whom Mr Bowen interviews tend to be at odds with their Salafi counterpartsâ€”advocates of the purist Sunni Islam associated with Saudi Arabiaâ€”who nowadays have a small but influential presence among Europeâ€™s Muslims.</seg>
