		<seg id="0">The UDF alliance speaks out and orders the New Centre party to stop using its acronym</seg>
		<seg id="1">The UDF alliance, controlled by FranÃ§ois Bayrou's Democratic Movement (MoDem), reacted on Friday to the buy-out bid made by the New Centre's president, HervÃ© Morin, for the acronym of the former Giscardian party, by ordering him not to use it under any circumstances, threatening legal action otherwise.</seg>
